divs: Sighting DetailsWaiting at the train station to picky my partner up, whilst looking into the sky as my partner is right into the UFO phenomenon, spotted a bright red orb come down and hover. Sent my partner a text to see if he could see the orb. His train arrived and before he got off the orb took off.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Niagara Park
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: bright glowing orb appeared from nowhere then disapppeard very quickly
